2 (b) The owner of an antique snowmobile may register
3 the snowmobile by submitting an application to the
4 department indicating that the snowmobile is operated
5 solely for the purposes of organized antique snowmobile
6 activities, parades, exhibitions, tours and other related
7 activities and will not be used for general snowmobile
8 uses.
