10 (c) Upon receipt of the registration fee pursuant to
11 W.S. 31-2-404(a)(iii), the selling agent shall issue to the
12 owner for each antique snowmobile a certificate of
13 registration, setting forth the facts in the application,
14 together with a numbered decal which shall bear a
15 distinctive number assigned to the snowmobile, which decal
16 shall at all times be prominently displayed on the
17 snowmobile. The registration expires upon transfer of
18 ownership of the antique snowmobile.
